{"tid":2320554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"楊明承認不小心駕駛等兩罪 但不承認拒絕提交血液樣本 排期明年三月審訊","createTime":"2020-12-11T02:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T06:58:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"86fdd9e176b465cd34a92a1e13bad13716e1ad62","tid":2320554,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12021&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ea1765f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12021</a><br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭 #提堂<br />\n#錢禮主任裁判官 #不是聲援<br />\n#20200808山頂 #不是手足<br />\n<br />\n🚹楊明/ 亦即林明樂(39) 💩回鄉證當八達通用嘅撐狗偽人🐶<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)雖有合理辯解而沒有提供樣本以作檢查呼氣測試但沒有提供血液樣本以作化驗<br />\n🙄不認罪🙄<br />\n<br />\n(2)不小心駕駛<br />\n😗認罪😗<br />\n<br />\n(3)車輛除頭尾擋風玻璃外，所有門窗玻璃附有膠貼及透光度不足 <br />\n😗認罪😗<br />\n<br />\n9位控方證人，用英文審訊，只傳召PW1,2,4,6,7，預審期一天。有<br />\n2段CCTV片段。<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n撐警無綫藝人、曾有醉酒駕駛前科的楊明，於8月8日在山頂馬己仙峽道發生交通意外，事發時他滿身酒氣未能自行上救護車，需要由兩名警員協助扶上救護車，送院治理後，警方以涉嫌「拒絕提供血液樣本」將其拘捕。//蘋果日報// <br />\n<br />\n🍾🍺🍾🍺🍾🍺🍾🍺🍾🍺<br />\n*案發日13年前嘅同一日，九龍城裁判法院裁判官直斥被告已經因多宗法庭案件做到「揚明聲」效果，當時辯方律師求請時指被告承諾日後酒不沾唇*<br />\n<br />\n於2021年3月2日0930東區七庭0930作英文審訊，現有條件保釋"},{"pid":"e6eb61def8fc0fe4a83165a331a93a1b5124b03e","tid":2320554,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acb0ebc049a534aa7d18c62c0a9a84577040bfb","tid":2320554,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:11:30.000Z","msg":"可能班差佬都冇叫佢吹波仔<br />\n情序出錯 冇罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c653ea994eedadfe3272865274f9be34963c5955","tid":2320554,"uid":31841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"楊sir話一邊個夠膽話二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f309eef504689e688e80d9d930d3d0433f49c81","tid":2320554,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de500221c9a35531874eae90c8c979b0f2f48da","tid":2320554,"uid":34811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"如果到時啲官冇調嚟調去<br />\n七庭會係鄭紀航<br />\n控罪(1)會不成立，(2)(3)可以罰款了事"},{"pid":"81835505c38e0ca34788c06b1c29cd887a85bfde","tid":2320554,"uid":221343,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:15:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔還押到3月呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53274719881e9934ffe7ed23b8f8a44256fb10c5","tid":2320554,"uid":57205,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"即係想話黑警唔洗佢吹波仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n射波俾班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafe4ef08de7a2d622b101a12d18ea3cff68fe08","tid":2320554,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0de500221c9a35531874eae90c8c979b0f2f48da","tid":2320554,"uid":34811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"如果到時啲官冇調嚟調去<br />\n七庭會係鄭紀航<br />\n控罪(1)會不成立，(2)(3)可以罰款了事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" cl